data.meta_description: Dlp 12.5 Rfp Responses Final - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Symantec is a global leader in information security and management that was founded in 1982 and has grown through acquisitions and partnerships. They entered the data loss prevention market in 2007 with the acquisition of Vontu. Symantec's corporate vision is to secure and manage the world's increasing amounts of information across various environments to address customers' challenges of securing business critical data across different devices and applications.
